00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:38.400
So I kind of try and
leave my ego at the door

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:41.980
when I go into somebody's space,
and it's all about that person.

00:03:41.980 --> 00:03:43.590
So in this instance,
it's about you.

00:03:43.590 --> 00:03:45.897
And you need to think
about, who am I?

00:03:45.897 --> 00:03:47.730
