We just have to check if
the microphone is working

00:36:31.050 --> 00:36:32.604
before we get it to you.

00:36:32.604 --> 00:36:33.520
AUDIENCE: I can shout.

00:36:33.520 --> 00:36:34.800
That's fine.

00:36:34.800 --> 00:36:35.000
KAROLINE O'SULLIVAN:
We just want

00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:36.958
to make sure that we hear
you on the recording.

00:36:36.958 --> 00:36:38.440
That's all.

00:36:38.440 --> 00:36:40.294
Thank you.

00:36:40.294 --> 00:36:41.710
LEONIE CORNELIUS:
Totally natural.

00:36:43.267 --> 00:36:44.850
KAROLINE O'SULLIVAN:
Oh, it's working.

00:36:44.850 --> 00:36:45.512
That's great.

00:36:45.512 --> 00:36:47.220
AUDIENCE: Thank you
so much for the talk.

