00:39:33.730 --> 00:39:36.070
AUDIENCE: So I'm moving
into a new house.

00:39:36.070 --> 00:39:39.580
We just bought a new
house just down the road.

00:39:39.580 --> 00:39:42.160
And we've got a roughly
